{'istart': 103, 'iend': 438, 'talk': 'Who does not know the deeds of the Sacred Ancestor? He began life as a minor official in Sishang. There gripping his sword, he slew a white serpent, the beginning of his struggle for the right. Speedily he mastered the empire; in three years had destroyed Qin and, in five, also Chu. Thus he set up a dynasty that shall endure forever!', 'context': ' said Dong Cheng, rather startled at the question. “'},
