{'istart': 21, 'iend': 216, 'talk': 'Zhuge Dan has set out to destroy Sima Zhao; Sun Chen of Wu has supported him with a large army; and Sima Zhao has led the army himself, bringing with him the Empress Dowager and the Ruler of Wei.', 'context': 'Then came the news: “'},
