{'istart': 26, 'iend': 198, 'talk': 'The Emperor is vicious and weak, depraved and foolish and unfit for his high office. Wherefore he must be deposed. Any of you who oppose will be punished as for conspiracy.', 'context': 'and addressed them thus: “'},
{'istart': 41, 'iend': 152, 'talk': 'How dare you utter such words? Our Emperor is very intelligent, and I will not support you. I would rather die.', 'context': 'It was High Minister Huan Yi, who said, “'},
