{'istart': 1, 'iend': 123, 'talk': 'You call these yours! Did you think that you alone held the secret? Since I have made it, of course I know the variations.', 'context': '“'},
{'istart': 1, 'iend': 22, 'talk': 'What of my evolution?', 'context': '“'},
