{'istart': 1, 'iend': 64, 'talk': 'Indeed a moment of pride had led me into the trap of Jiang Wei,', 'context': '“'},
{'istart': 1, 'iend': 55, 'talk': 'How did you know exactly where to strike in that maze?', 'context': '“'},
{'istart': 20, 'iend': 278, 'talk': "In my youth I studied tactics and was friendly with Shi Guangyuan and Cui Zhouping. They explained that formation to me. Jiang Wei used what is known as 'The Serpent Coil,' and the only way to break it is to attack the head, which I saw was in the northwest.", 'context': 'Sima Wang replied, “'},
