{'istart': 1, 'iend': 138, 'talk': 'Tomorrow you shall contend with him, and while his attention is engaged, I will attack the rear of Qishan, and we will recover our camps.', 'context': '“'},
{'istart': 33, 'iend': 348, 'talk': 'In the secret book that I received from the Prime Minister, the variations of the formation are three hundred and sixty−five, corresponding to the circuit of the heavens. This challenge from them is as one going to teach hewing to the God of Carpenters. I think some ruse lies behind this. Can you guess what it is?', 'context': 'Jiang Wei said to his officers, “'},
